contentrichtext.text: '''Merritt''' is the name of an unincorporated community in the State of [[South Dakota]] in the United States of America. It lies in [[Pennington County, South Dakota|Pennington County]] and [[Lawrence County, South Dakota]]. It is located at {{coord|44|08|27|N|103|34|07|W|type:city_region:US-SD|display=inline,title}}.<ref>USGS [[Geographic Names Information System]], [http://geonames.usgs.gov/pls/gnispublic/f?p=115:3:4301394974186247::NO:3:P3_FID,P3_TITLE:1262057%2CMerritt entry for Merritt] </ref> ==References== <references/> [[Category:Unincorporated communities in South Dakota]]
